devnote-732739:
Dear store manager, 
Welcome to this fantasy island floating among the stars. This is the "Sea Beast Restaurant" - a spiritual haven where dreams are baked by moonlight and warmed by tides. 
Here you will meet: 
🌊 The polar bear chef who can sing ancient fishing songs; 
🐚The harp seal is good at catching shells; 
🌌 Leviathan customers dining under the stars; 
Every character in the restaurant, every dish, and even every sound of the waves is the result of countless discussions, adjustments and optimizations by our team. There are also several carefully designed realistic Easter eggs in the game, connecting the virtual world with reality. The cat "Juan Juan" who is responsible for collecting tips in the restaurant is based on a three-legged unicorn cat rescued by our team. There are also some characters of sea monster customers and employees, which are inspired by the pets of team members. 
We hope that "Sea Beast Restaurant" can become a bright spot in your busy life. When you realize your childhood dreams and gain full happiness in the game, you can also find the long-lost confidence and courage in the real world. 
This is not an urgent business game, but a journey of self-healing. When you serve "Memory Sparkling Drinks" to customers, you may also think of the small shop with warm lights on the corner of your childhood; when you expand the underwater garden, you may be completing an unfinished dream with yourself in the parallel world. 
We always believe that games are not only a refuge from reality, but also an extension of life. We will continue to use love as a driving force to continuously improve game content and optimize the experience. We look forward to your feedback and let’s work together to make “Sea Beast Restaurant” even better.

